{"_id":"1Z7lztM5GGme2Zaa","name":"Survival Guide","content":"<p><img style=\"border:0px;text-decoration:none;outline:none;display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" src=\"modules/swademacros/images/nottoday.webp\" width=\"300\" height=\"154\" /></p>\n<p> </p>\n<table style=\"height:512px;width:99.6506%;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\">\n<tbody>\n<tr style=\"height:17px\">\n<td style=\"height:17px;width:11.7144%;text-align:center\" colspan=\"2\"><strong>Problem:</strong></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;width:19.5118%;height:17px\" colspan=\"2\"><strong>And…</strong></td>\n<td style=\"width:12.0926%;height:17px;text-align:center\"><strong>Then Try To…</strong></td>\n<td style=\"width:45.5237%;height:17px;text-align:center\"><strong>Game Effect</strong></td>\n<td style=\"width:2.6695%;height:17px;text-align:center\"><strong>Helps:</strong></td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:21px\">\n<td style=\"height:359px;text-align:center;width:4.79839%\" rowspan=\"9\"><strong>You can’t hit the foe</strong></td>\n<td style=\"height:161px;text-align:center;width:6.91604%\" rowspan=\"4\"><strong>High Parry</strong></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;width:19.5118%;height:55px\" colspan=\"2\">Your team outnumbers the foe</td>\n<td style=\"width:12.0926%;height:55px;text-align:center\">@Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.hdXOHCe38O8KGyUz]{Ganging Up}</td>\n<td style=\"width:45.5237%;height:55px;text-align:center\">\n<p>+1 Fighting for each additional non-Stunned ally in melee with the target (max +4).</p>\n<p>Lower this bonus by 1 point for every enemy adjacent to the target (min 0).</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:2.6695%;height:55px;text-align:center\">Team</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:17px\">\n<td style=\"text-align:center;width:19.5118%;height:55px\" colspan=\"2\">You are pretty strong (high Strength), you can move before acting and/or you have a shield</td>\n<td style=\"width:12.0926%;height:55px;text-align:center\">@Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.GsNwqTjOQLVbQras]{Push} to knock them  @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.JhBfyamFYWMA4T93]{Prone}</td>\n<td style=\"width:45.5237%;height:55px;text-align:center\">\n<p>Opposed Strength or Athletic (each one chooses) roll (+2 if moved 2” before pushing, +Shield Parry Bonus): push 1”, 2” with a raise.</p>\n<p>The foe also rolls Athletics (-2 if the pusher raised) to avoid falling PRONE.</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:2.6695%;height:55px;text-align:center\">Team</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:17px\">\n<td style=\"text-align:center;width:19.5118%;height:17px\" colspan=\"2\">You are OK with lowering your defense</td>\n<td style=\"width:12.0926%;height:17px;text-align:center\">Do a @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.iGSH4rtlKNSlJJff]{Wild Attack}</td>\n<td style=\"width:45.5237%;height:17px;text-align:center\">+2 Fighting, +2 melee damage, but you are now VULNERABLE</td>\n<td style=\"width:2.6695%;height:17px;text-align:center\">You</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:17px\">\n<td style=\"text-align:center;width:19.5118%;height:34px\" colspan=\"2\">You are using a melee weapon</td>\n<td style=\"width:12.0926%;height:34px;text-align:center\">Switch to RANGED ATTACKS</td>\n<td style=\"width:45.5237%;height:34px;text-align:center\">An enemy without COVER or similar has a target number of 4 to be hit by a ranged attack. Change up to 2 weapons as a free action once per turn.</td>\n<td style=\"width:2.6695%;height:34px;text-align:center\">You</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:34px\">\n<td style=\"text-align:center;width:6.91604%;height:68px\" rowspan=\"2\"><strong>Great Penalties for a Ranged Attack</strong></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;width:19.5118%;height:34px\" colspan=\"2\">You can miss a turn and you can stand still in your position</td>\n<td style=\"width:12.0926%;text-align:center;height:34px\">@Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.Fxh6qdmOiHPAO0VK]{Aim}</td>\n<td style=\"width:45.5237%;text-align:center;height:34px\">Spend the entire turn (movement included) to lower by up to 4 points of penalties (from COVER, CALLED SHOT, Range…) OR add +2 to the first ranged attack of the next round.</td>\n<td style=\"width:2.6695%;text-align:center;height:34px\">You</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:34px\">\n<td style=\"text-align:center;width:19.5118%;height:34px\" colspan=\"2\">You are using a ranged weapon, and you can shorten the distance to engage in melee</td>\n<td style=\"width:12.0926%;text-align:center;height:34px\">Switch to MELEE ATTACKS</td>\n<td style=\"width:45.5237%;text-align:center;height:34px\">An enemy with COVER or PRONE can still be hit without penalties with Fighting. Change up to 2 weapons as a free action once per turn.</td>\n<td style=\"width:2.6695%;text-align:center;height:34px\">You</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:17px\">\n<td style=\"text-align:center;height:130px;width:6.91604%\" rowspan=\"3\"><strong>One of the motives above, or both</strong></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;width:19.5118%;height:34px\" colspan=\"2\">You can help an ally (“he has a weak spot there!”, trip the foe, “JUST DO IT!”)</td>\n<td style=\"width:12.0926%;text-align:center;height:34px\">@Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.TFR8EmfT9ci1gBEy]{Support} an ally’s combat skill</td>\n<td style=\"width:45.5237%;text-align:center;height:34px\">Describe how you help your ally’s Trait and roll your relevant Skill to give them +1 with a success, +2 with a raise (max +4).</td>\n<td style=\"width:2.6695%;text-align:center;height:34px\">Ally</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:17px\">\n<td style=\"text-align:center;width:19.5118%;height:79px\" colspan=\"2\">You can hinder your foe through a clever tactic (throw sand in their eyes, a feint, ”look behind you”, provocations, war cries)</td>\n<td style=\"width:12.0926%;text-align:center;height:79px\">@Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.2aAyYC6n07MrZ47O]{Test} your foe to make them  @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.vuud75GDkKL3NW10]{Distracted and Vulnerable}</td>\n<td style=\"width:45.5237%;text-align:center;height:79px\">\n<p>Describe a TEST and roll a relevant Skill against the foe’s linked Attribute.</p>\n<p>Success: the foe is DISTRACTED or VULNERABLE, your choice.</p>\n<p>Raise: the foe is also SHAKEN.</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:2.6695%;text-align:center;height:79px\">Team</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:17px\">\n<td style=\"text-align:center;width:19.5118%;height:17px\" colspan=\"2\">You are OK with sacrificing your movement</td>\n<td style=\"width:12.0926%;text-align:center;height:17px\">@Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.od3tHNJTS8Ma4n2o]{GRAPPLE} your foe</td>\n<td style=\"width:45.5237%;text-align:center;height:17px\">\n<p>@Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.sTArFBzbesQkjLVg]{Bound and Entangled}</p>\n<p>Athletics (or Strength -2) vs Athletics (or Strength -2) to @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.sTArFBzbesQkjLVg]{ENTANGLE}the target, or to @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.sTArFBzbesQkjLVg]{BOUND} (the grappler is also VULNERABLE) with a raise.</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:2.6695%;text-align:center;height:17px\">Team</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:17px\">\n<td style=\"text-align:center;height:51px;width:11.7144%\" colspan=\"2\" rowspan=\"2\"><strong>You can’t damage the foe enough (High Toughness*)</strong></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;width:19.5118%;height:34px\" colspan=\"2\">You aren’t having problems hitting the foe</td>\n<td style=\"width:12.0926%;text-align:center;height:34px\">Do a @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.OpzGhU3fssihv5ds]{CALLED SHOT} against a weak point</td>\n<td style=\"width:45.5237%;text-align:center;height:34px\">Limb: -2 (may @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.GkQ6WX0VSFHdTS3N]{Disarm}; Hand: -4 (may @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.GkQ6WX0VSFHdTS3N]{Disarm}), Head/Vitals: -4 (+4 damage), Unarmored Area: -? (damage ignores Armor).</td>\n<td style=\"width:2.6695%;text-align:center;height:34px\">You</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:17px\">\n<td style=\"text-align:center;width:19.5118%;height:17px\" colspan=\"2\">You are OK with lowering your defense</td>\n<td style=\"width:12.0926%;text-align:center;height:17px\">Do a @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.iGSH4rtlKNSlJJff]{Wild Attack}</td>\n<td style=\"width:45.5237%;text-align:center;height:17px\">+2 Fighting, +2 melee damage, but you are now VULNERABLE</td>\n<td style=\"width:2.6695%;text-align:center;height:17px\">You</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:17px\">\n<td style=\"text-align:center;height:85px;width:11.7144%\" colspan=\"2\" rowspan=\"4\"><strong>You are going to die soon if you keep standing there!</strong></td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center;width:19.5118%;height:17px\" colspan=\"2\">You are engaged in melee and you don’t want to risk rolling your dice</td>\n<td style=\"width:12.0926%;text-align:center;height:17px\">@Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.qfAkQVB9LbFFdDQ3]{WITHDRAW} WITHDRAW to fight another day!</td>\n<td style=\"width:45.5237%;text-align:center;height:17px\">Each non-Shaken and non-Stunned adjacent enemy receives a free attack against the hero that flees from melee. You may use your turn to DEFEND (see pag. 100) in order to gain +4 Parry and move your normal Pace (but not run).</td>\n<td style=\"width:2.6695%;text-align:center;height:17px\">You</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:17px\">\n<td style=\"text-align:center;width:10.2335%;height:34px\" rowspan=\"2\">You are engaged by a single enemy…</td>\n<td style=\"width:9.2783%;text-align:center;height:17px\">…but you are pretty Strong (high Strength) and/or you have a shield</td>\n<td style=\"width:12.0926%;text-align:center;height:17px\">@Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.GsNwqTjOQLVbQras]{Push} to make your foe non adjacent, then move</td>\n<td style=\"width:45.5237%;text-align:center;height:17px\">Opposed Strength or Athletic (each one chooses) roll ( +Shield Parry Bonus): push 1”, 2” with a raise. The foe also rolls Athletics (-2 if the pusher raised) to avoid falling PRONE.</td>\n<td style=\"width:2.6695%;text-align:center;height:17px\">You, Team</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:17px\">\n<td style=\"width:9.2783%;text-align:center;height:17px\">…but you can hinder your foe through a clever tactic</td>\n<td style=\"width:12.0926%;text-align:center;height:17px\">@Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.2aAyYC6n07MrZ47O]{Test} to make your foe @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.vuud75GDkKL3NW10]{Distracted and Vulnerable} or even SHAKEN, then move</td>\n<td style=\"width:45.5237%;text-align:center;height:17px\">\n<p>Describe a TEST and roll a relevant Skill against the foe’s linked Attribute.</p>\n<p>Success: the foe is DISTRACTED or VULNERABLE, your choice.</p>\n<p>Raise: the foe is also SHAKEN.</p>\n</td>\n<td style=\"width:2.6695%;text-align:center;height:17px\">You, Team</td>\n</tr>\n<tr style=\"height:34px\">\n<td style=\"text-align:center;width:19.5118%;height:34px\" colspan=\"2\">The foes target you from afar</td>\n<td style=\"width:12.0926%;text-align:center;height:34px\">Find @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.854By7DpYevCCEfJ]{Cover and Obstacles} or move then drop @Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.JhBfyamFYWMA4T93]{Prone}</td>\n<td style=\"width:45.5237%;text-align:center;height:34px\">Attackers subtract from -2 to -8 to their ranged attacks against you, depending on the COVER you found, PRONE is a -4 COVER against ranged attacks from 3”+.</td>\n<td style=\"width:2.6695%;text-align:center;height:34px\">You</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p> </p>\n<p>*Many of the combat maneuvers that assist in hitting a foe also help deal damage, as they increase the chance of getting a raise and extra +1d6 damage (or they make an opponent SHAKEN).</p>\n<p> </p>\n<ul>\n<li>RECOVER from being SHAKEN: Roll Spirit at the start of your turn, or spend a Benny at any time (pag. 94).</li>\n<li>SOAK incoming Wounds: Spend a Benny and roll Vigor to negate one wound for every success and raise (pag. 96).</li>\n</ul>\n<p> </p>\n<ul>\n<li>BOUND: Cannot move, cannot do other physical actions except trying to break free, DISTRACTED and VULNERABLE as long as they remain Bound. Use an action to roll Athletics (or Strength -2) and become ENTANGLED with a success, or break free with a raise (p. 98).</li>\n<li>DISTRACTED: -2 to the character’s roll until the end of their next turn (p. 100).</li>\n<li>ENTANGLED: Cannot move and is DISTRACTED as long as they remain Entangled. Use an action to roll Athletics (or Strength -2) and break free (p. 98).</li>\n<li>PRONE: -2 Parry, -2 Fighting, -4 to be hit from range 3”+ (doesn’t stack with COVER), -4 damage from attack with Area of Effects, use 2” of Pace to crawl 1” or to stand up (p. 104).</li>\n<li>SHAKEN: Can only perform free actions (including normal movement, plus eventually running). Recover from being SHAKEN as free action with a Spirit roll at the start of the character’s turn (p. 94).</li>\n<li>STUNNED: Can’t move nor take actions, is PRONE, attacks against him get THE DROP (p. 100). Each turn make a Vigor roll to recover: success recovers but is DISTRACTED and VULNERABLE, raise no ill effects.</li>\n<li>VULNERABLE: +2 to every roll against them until the end of their next turn (pag. 100).</li>\n</ul>\n<p> </p>\n<p>by u/anri11, Silent Mask</p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"tckKxzbezKvre3KI":3},"flags":{"core":{"sourceId":"JournalEntry.olGfj6mnx3OxsvtJ"}}}
{"_id":"PwzyJrlKprqNeJIz","name":"Macros for SWADE","content":"<h1>Macros for SWADE</h1>\n<p> </p>\n<h2>Macro Managers</h2>\n<p>You can use the managers to open a menu with the main macros for each role. It'll only work after you import all macros.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>GM - Macro Manager</p>\n<p><img src=\"modules/swademacros/docs/gmmacromanager.webp\" width=\"250\" height=\"169\" /></p>\n<p>Player - Macro Manager</p>\n<p><img src=\"modules/swademacros/docs/playermacromanager.webp\" width=\"250\" height=\"132\" /></p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><img src=\"icons/sundries/gaming/playing-cards.webp\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" /> Chase</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Run the macro.</li>\n<li>You can select a Deck. You can set to dogfight.</li>\n</ol>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img src=\"modules/swademacros/docs/chase.webp\" width=\"398\" height=\"415\" /></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Rules</p>\n<p>@Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.nB1vsvPTn5jSRG6v]{Chases and Vehicles}</p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><img src=\"icons/weapons/thrown/dynamite-simple-brown.webp\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" /> Deviation</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Run the macro and it will tell will where to land the template.</li>\n</ol>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Rules</p>\n<p>@Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.xxEcWExtn36PPxg0]{Area Effect Attacks}</p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><img src=\"icons/creatures/mammals/wolf-shadow-black.webp\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" /> Gang Up</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Select one token.</li>\n<li>Target another token.</li>\n<li>Run the macro. It'll calculate the Ganging Up bonus. </li>\n</ol>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Important</p>\n<p>This macro uses token disposition to indentify friend from foe. Be sure to set them property.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Module</p>\n<p>Token Faction is recommended.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Rules</p>\n<p>@Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.hdXOHCe38O8KGyUz]{Ganging Up}</p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><img src=\"icons/commodities/biological/tentacle-purple-white.webp\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" /> Grappling</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Select one token.</li>\n<li>Target another token.</li>\n<li>Run the macro. It'll calculate the Ganging Up bonus + Size/Scale bonus. </li>\n</ol>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Important</p>\n<p>This macro uses token disposition to indentify friend from foe. Be sure to set them property.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Module</p>\n<p>Token Faction is recommended.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Rules</p>\n<p>@Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.od3tHNJTS8Ma4n2o]{Grappling}</p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><img src=\"icons/magic/life/cross-area-circle-green-white.webp\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" /> Healing</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Select a token. Run the macro.</li>\n<li>Natural Healing and Skill Healing</li>\n</ol>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Rules</p>\n<p>@Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.gCrNh35pUQHaVN4J]{Healing}</p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><img src=\"icons/environment/people/charge.webp\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" /> Mass Battle</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Run the macro.</li>\n<li>Fill the data.</li>\n<li>Battle!</li>\n</ol>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img src=\"modules/swademacros/docs/massbattle.webp\" width=\"280\" height=\"318\" /></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Rules</p>\n<p>@Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.IJkWxV4kddDaU0Gl]{Mass Battles}</p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><img src=\"icons/magic/time/arrows-circling-pink.webp\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" /> Next Turn</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>It'll skip the current turn if are in combat.</li>\n</ol>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><img src=\"icons/creatures/mammals/bull-horned-blue.webp\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" /> Push</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Select a token and target another one.</li>\n<li>You can add the Running bonus. Select the skill to roll and add parry from shields.</li>\n</ol>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img src=\"modules/swademacros/docs/pushmacro.webp\" width=\"300\" height=\"144\" /></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Rules</p>\n<p>@Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.GsNwqTjOQLVbQras]{Push}</p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><img src=\"icons/magic/time/clock-stopwatch-white-blue.webp\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" /> Quick Combat</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Run the macro.</li>\n<li>It'll select ALL tokens in the active scene, send them to combat tracker and draw the cards.</li>\n</ol>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><img src=\"icons/skills/movement/arrow-upward-yellow.webp\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" /> Raise Calculator</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Run the macro.</li>\n<li>It'll update the success level as you type.</li>\n</ol>\n<p> </p>\n<p><img src=\"modules/swademacros/docs/raisecalc.webp\" width=\"250\" height=\"163\" /></p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><img src=\"icons/tools/hand/scale-balances-merchant-brown.webp\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" /> Size/Scale Calculator</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Select a token.</li>\n<li>Target another one.</li>\n<li>Run the macro.</li>\n</ol>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Rules</p>\n<p>@Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.mbP0fwcquD98QtwX]{Size and Scale}</p>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><img src=\"icons/magic/control/fear-fright-white.webp\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" /> Unshaken</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Select a token.</li>\n<li>Run the macro.</li>\n<li>If the token is shaken it will offer to roll spirit and spend a benny on failure.</li>\n<li>If the token is unshaken it will set the Shaken status to it.</li>\n</ol>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Rules</p>\n<p>@Compendium[swade-core-rules.swade-rules.30TJKevSbgxK6jQy]{Damage Effects}</p>\n<p> </p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"tckKxzbezKvre3KI":3},"flags":{}}
{"name":"Macros for Settings","content":"<p> </p>\n<h1>Sprawlrunners</h1>\n<p> </p>\n<h2><img src=\"icons/commodities/treasure/puzzle-box-glowing-blue.webp\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" /> LP Check</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Run the macro.</li>\n<li>All players conected with a character selected will have their Logistics Points accounted from the itens.</li>\n</ol>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Requirements</p>\n<p>You must set Additional Stats in System Settings like the image:</p>\n<p><img src=\"modules/swademacros/docs/sprawllpcheck.webp\" width=\"600\" height=\"547\" /></p>\n<p>Then, you must enable it in the Actor Sheet.</p>\n<p><img src=\"modules/swademacros/docs/sprawllpcheck2.webp\" width=\"625\" height=\"697\" /></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Sprawlrunners--FoundryVTT-Module</p>\n<p>https://www.drivethrurpg.com/product/351063/Sprawlrunners--FoundryVTT-Module</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Rule</p>\n<p>@Compendium[sprawl-core-rules.sprawl-rules.jhEs3al7qA4sAwaa]{Logistics Points}</p>","folder":null,"sort":0,"permission":{"default":0,"tckKxzbezKvre3KI":3},"flags":{},"_id":"ZxL99P27CzdftRIS"}
